Hypothesis and reference text are sanitized Lorem Ipsum
(https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lorem_ipsum)

SCLITE is part of the SCTK toolkit (https://github.com/usnistgov/SCTK)
developed by NIST. The license can be found at
http://www.nist.gov/open/license.cfm.

The following calls were used to extract the relevant results. Divisions
convert the "percentage" to fractions.

sclite -r ref.trn -h hyp.trn -i swb > sclite_out.txt
cat sclite_out.txt | grep '^ *| [0-9]' | tr '|' ' ' | awk '{print $1"-"$1,$8/100}' > per_utt.txt
cat sclite_out.txt | grep 'Sum/Avg' | awk '{print $10/100}' > total.txt